[Algebra, intAlgebra, stringAlgebra, dictionaryIdentity, dictionaryZero, dictionaryCombine](typeclass-dictionary-lib.ssc)

# Imported dictionary value flow

```scalascript
val intAlias = dictionaryIdentity(intAlgebra)
val stringAlias = dictionaryIdentity(stringAlgebra)

println(intAlias.label)
println(dictionaryZero(intAlias))
println(dictionaryCombine(intAlias, 3, 4))
println(stringAlias.label)
println("[" + dictionaryZero(stringAlias) + "]")
println(dictionaryCombine(stringAlias, "left", "-right"))
println(List(intAlias, stringAlias).map(dictionary => dictionary.label).mkString("|"))
println(intAlgebra.combine(8, 9))
println(summon[Algebra[Int]].combine(10, 11))
```
